ations tabled in 1998.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aNATURE / Environmental Conservation & Protection.2bisacsh1 aGlover, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlover, David, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHon, Priscilla M.L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJessup, Timothy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJessup, Timothy, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOthman, Jamal, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuitenbeek, Jack, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSalim, Emil, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchweithelm, James, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShahwahid, Mohd H.O, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Archive (pre 2000) eBook Packagez978311064968008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertISEAS Archive eBook-Package 1970-1999z978311060669040uhttps://doi.org/10.1355/978981230577040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789812305770423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789812305770.jpg  a978-3-11-060669-0  ISEAS Archive eBook-Package 1970-1999c1970d1999  a978-3-11-064968-0  Asian Studies Archive (pre 2000) eBook Package  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK